This paper deals with the analysis of microblogging platforms and the application of representation learning models for tasks like sentiment analysis, semantic textual similarity computation, hashtag prediction, etc. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the categories of Computational Linguistics (cs.CL), Social and Information Networks (cs.SI), Machine Learning (cs.LG), Information Retrieval (cs.IR), and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI).
